{"tid":1408424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台發出八號熱帶氣旋警告信號","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:26:00.000Z","uid":27697,"like":1,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d66c0f4e57684ea2f7fdcea31e36e4a1bcd9f02","tid":1408424,"uid":27697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"強烈熱帶風暴天鵝報告（一）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　香港天文台昨晚（八月四日）九時四十分發出八號熱帶氣旋警告信號。預料強烈熱帶風暴天鵝將於未來數小時非常接近本港。<br />\n<br />\n　　山頂纜車服務以及大部分巴士服務已經停止。<br />\n<br />\n　　由昨晚九時至十一時，三班抵港及一班離港航機取消，十二班抵港及四班離港航機延誤。<br />\n<br />\n　　民政事務總署在各區共開放二十四個臨時庇護站，截至下午十一時三十分，共有一百一十九人入住。<br />\n<br />\n　　暫時未有任何水浸和山泥傾瀉報告。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２００９年８月５日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間０時０７分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200908/05/P200908050003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200908%2F05%2FP200908050003.htm&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=7509a1b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200908/05/P200908050003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a094950c9f363761ffe113bf1114d87968a164f","tid":1408424,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個天都嬲嬲豬"},{"pid":"1f939beda263009a16745cfea596b32e1e419364","tid":1408424,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 北極有企鵝<br />\n<br />\n舊聞"},{"pid":"83102b02e9ac4c8c68fb3fcc81e7da124f7c79d0","tid":1408424,"uid":27697,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"打風唔好返工啦咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6a93d0782ca228085eb55c8f5a85767098e930","tid":1408424,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24078c863052c76e59ea50875d9270c71af3b1ef","tid":1408424,"uid":1070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"block"},{"pid":"6693a9f6251c683a566d9388ac1377c5dc2b1946","tid":1408424,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"２００９年８月５日（星期三）<br />\n<br />\nBlock，上一頁"},{"pid":"fa42901b3fd0e649a4543914e5eae8ade4e4a4d7","tid":1408424,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:20:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b35fa4caee9aa6f9e1e7d8dadb8edfb3b3ff14f1","tid":1408424,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"做咩事"},{"pid":"4ec52e829e4a17a4f17547e691045a474f1b969a","tid":1408424,"uid":185092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ff4e778d0c649a15d0ef08980c97340a6177540e","tid":1408424,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"10年前... blocked, 上一頁"},{"pid":"54e903affcee567c103b1a9cd1f7e2f0eaeb6b55","tid":1408424,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"blocked, 免推"},{"pid":"fbad87e3a2f1d5c522414e73da1f805dd1e67e7c","tid":1408424,"uid":27697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見上星期啲人屌港鐵不合作運動、第日打風就唔屌，所以想搵返篇舊聞去畀籍口想返工嘅人罷工姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile